The words were hard to speak at first.  The numbing in his arm seemed to be slowly spreading to other parts of his body.  Twyll was afraid he would die before he finished but that made him that much more determined to persist.<br>
<br>
&quot;We were at the Minotaur caves.  I had been elected to go in as scout.&quot;<br>
<br>
