<br>
&quot;Yes, that's right.  Some of us believe in Meldrath and want him for our king.  The Asylum was never truly done away with.  It was only believed by the Eldritch Collective that it was.  For now die and know your last words were for nothing.  Jaroo will be found and brought back to us.&quot;<br>
<br>
As Twyll's eyes closed for the final time he heard nothing but laughter.<br>
<br>
