<br>
Tobon saw a makeshift bed no doubt tinkered hurriedly with Jaroo laying on it unconscious or asleep, he couldn't tell which.  Digetha Chogaller looked up from beside the bed at Tobon with a sad look apparent on her face.  She stood and approached him.<br>
<br>
&quot;There doesn't seem to be much I can do.&quot;  She said.  &quot;My spells don't seem to be doing much good.  I've done the best I can.&quot;<br>
<br>
