<br>
&quot;How did you escape then?&quot; inquired Manik.<br>
<br>
&quot;I don't know.  The Minotaurs seemed to not be watching me too carefully, but when I ran they chased after me.  I'm not even sure what steps he was talking about.  Mostly it's a blur.  Like my mind won't remember.&quot;<br>
<br>
Manik looked thoughtful at the young gnome.<br>
<br>
&quot;What matters is that your safe.&quot;  Tobon smiled.  &quot;Will you be staying now that your back or leaving again?&quot;<br>
<br>
