<br>
&quot;I am not a wizard any longer.&quot;  Jaroo said looking him dead in the eye.  &quot;Nor will I be a warrior.  What I do need is to fight with the ability to cast.&quot;  Continuing out the door he finished with.  &quot;Thanks for the offer though.&quot;<br>
<br>
