<br>
&quot;I think you need to go and see Iony, Tobon.  She told me she may know what has afflicted him.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;It's not over yet, Digetha?  I'll go right now.  Besides, it would be good to see Jaroo when he joins the church.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;I'll join you.  We have some things to discus.&quot; said Manik not hearing Tobon's sigh as he followed him out the door.<br>
